Commentary: >
  Recited by the followers of Samaveda in the daily noon-time Sandhya worship;
  after the Gayatri-repetitions are over, the worshipper looks at the Sun and
  recites this (note by V. Raghavan). See GÃ¢yatrip. 317.
Format: verse
